{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/bona-vacantia/about/publication-scheme","content_id":"5f55f524-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","description":"This publication scheme sets out the types of information we usually publish and explains how to get hold of that information. \r\n","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><h2 id=\"types-of-information-we-publish\">Types of information we publish</h2>\n\n<p>We publish information about:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>who we are and what we do</li>\n  <li>what we spend and how we spend it</li>\n  <li>what our priorities are</li>\n  <li>our policies and procedures</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>We also publish a list of unclaimed estates and, at our own discretion, FOI responses in estates cases to assist kin in locating their entitlement.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"how-to-get-information\">How to get information</h2>\n\n<p>We publish information on this website. Copies of our annual accounts, FOI responses and the unclaimed estates list can be found with our <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?&amp;departments%5B%5D=bona-vacantia\" class=\"govuk-link\">publications</a>.</p>\n\n<p>If you have any queries on the information we publish you can contact us at:</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact contact\" id=\"contact_1450\">\n    <p class=\"govuk-body\">Government Legal Department</p>\n\n    <p class=\"govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-4\">\n      Governnment Legal Department (BVD)<br>1 Ruskin Square<br>Croydon<br>CR0 2WF\n    </p>\n\n    <div>\n        <p class=\"govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-4\">\n          Email <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"mailto:bvinfo@governmentlegal.gov.uk\">bvinfo@governmentlegal.gov.uk</a>\n        </p>\n\n\n        <p class=\"govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-4\">\n          Switchboard 020 7210 4700\n        </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <p class=\"govuk-body\">Please use this email address for all general enquiries about the work of the Bona Vacantia Division.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2013-12-10T14:16:00Z"}],"headers":[{"id":"types-of-information-we-publish","level":2,"text":"Types of information we publish"},{"id":"how-to-get-information","level":2,"text":"How to get information"}],"organisation":"c9109663-0128-4db4-b513-a9cdfb691034","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"publication_scheme","first_published_at":"2013-12-10T14:16:00+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/bona-vacantia/about/publication-scheme","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/bona-vacantia/about/publication-scheme","base_path":"/government/organisations/bona-vacantia/about/publication-scheme","content_id":"5f55f524-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","document_type":"publication_scheme","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2013-12-10T14:16:00Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"Publication scheme","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/bona-vacantia/about/publication-scheme","withdrawn":false}],"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT564","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/bona-vacantia","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/bona-vacantia","base_path":"/government/organisations/bona-vacantia","content_id":"c9109663-0128-4db4-b513-a9cdfb691034","details":{"acronym":"BVD","brand":"attorney-generals-office","default_news_image":null,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Bona Vacantia"},"organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null}},"document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Bona Vacantia","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/bona-vacantia","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","phase":"live","public_updated_at":"2013-12-10T14:16:00+00:00","publishing_app":"whitehall","publishing_request_id":"21-1747303165.377-10.13.20.98-2487","pu